### 1. Create User (Shipping Line)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "shipping_admin_1",
  "email": "admin@shipping.com",
  "password": "strongPassword123",
  "role": "SHIPPING_LINE"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "shipping_admin_1",
  "password": "strongPassword123"
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token); %}

### 3. Register Vessel
POST http://localhost:8080/api/vessels
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "name": "Ever Given",
  "imoNumber": "IMO9811000",
  "capacity": 20000
}

### 4. Create Vessel Schedule
POST http://localhost:8080/api/vessels/schedules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "vessel": { "id": 1 },
  "arrivalTime": "2024-05-01T10:00:00",
  "departureTime": "2024-05-05T10:00:00",
  "status": "SCHEDULED"
}

### 5. Register Container (ARRIVED automatically)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/containers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "containerNumber": "MSKU1234567",
  "size": "40ft",
  "weight": 15000,
  "vesselSchedule": { "id": 1 }
}

### 6. Create Booking
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "bookedBy": { "id": 1 },
  "container": { "id": 1 },
  "destination": "Warehouse A"
}

### 7. File Customs Declaration
POST http://localhost:8080/api/customs/declaration
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "container": { "id": 1 },
  "hsCode": "847130",
  "declaredValue": 50000.0
}

### 8. Clear Container
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/customs/declaration/1/clear?remarks=All%20Clear
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 9. Perform GATE_OUT target container
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/containers/1/status?status=GATE_OUT
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 10. Update transit -> delivered
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/containers/1/status?status=DELIVERED
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 11. Calculate Fees
POST http://localhost:8080/api/fees/calculate?containerId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 12. Fetch Movement Logs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/movement-logs/container/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
